# Changelog

- Added fixed `index.html` addressing hover region, disabled button clarity, and modal/backdrop/scroll behavior.
- Added Playwright tests (`tests/ui.spec.ts`) and config (`playwright.config.ts`).
- Created scripts: `setup.sh`, `run.sh`, `test.sh` with robust server handling.
- Added Dockerfile, .dockerignore, tsconfig, and project README.
- Ensured reproducible setup, run, and test workflows.
